snippet.title: LEGO Brawls Jurassic World Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Jurassic World comes to LEGO Brawls in an update for the ages! All-new Isla Nublar level, amazing dino powerups, new Brawls champion Owen Grady and even more Jurassic content in our first ever Brawls season. Collect all the new content before it’s extinct!

Welcome to the LEGO Gaming channel! That’s right, a channel dedicated to all things LEGO Games. How awesome is that?! Hold on to your controllers as we take you through a world of exclusive previews, developer walkthroughs, trailers, retro LEGO games, and exciting event coverage!

Subscribe to be notified of new videos each week: https://www.youtube.com/LEGOGaming
